article_title: Ship carrying undelivered aid for Gaza returns to Cyprus.
sentence: A  cargo  ship  carrying  240  tonnes  of  food  meant  for  Gaza  has  returned  to  Cyprus,  after  Israeli  air  strikes  killed  seven  World  Central  Kitchen  aid  workers.

article_title: Ship carrying undelivered aid for Gaza returns to Cyprus.
sentence: The  aid  workers  from  WCK  had  just  finished  unloading  100  tonnes  of  aid  from  a  barge  -  also  sent  from  Cyprus  -  when  they  were  killed  on  Monday  night.
